sources.description:
In 2038 earth reaches a cosmic tipping point and enters a mysterious universe. To perpetuate the old order, the government builds a gigantic sky-wall and engages in wars. In this dystopian wonderland, Denise walks on thin ice to believe in her future, spurred on by Tom, a caretaker, who promises that a renaissance is on its way.

2024.  Stars: Michael Madsen, Judd Nelson, William Baldwin
